{
    "analysis": "From the previous aggregates we confirmed telemetry is well-formed and contains 25 samples per series spanning 2024-01-24 22:47:00 to 2024-01-24 23:11:00 UTC. Candidate hotspots from that pass include ts-travel2-service (high CPU, socket, mem) and services with high log.row_count (e.g., ts-basic-service, ts-order-service). However, the allowed root-cause components for this task are limited to: ts-auth-service, ts-order-service, ts-route-service, ts-train-service, ts-travel-service. We must therefore restrict further analysis to those five services. Next we need to follow the prescribed order: calculate global thresholds using the full series for each component-KPI (P95), then filter to the incident window (2024-01-24 22:44:04 to 2024-01-24 23:14:04 UTC) and detect anomalies that breach thresholds during the incident window. ",
